msgid "Bayes factor contours breaks could not be parsed into numbers."
msgstr "Patahan kontur faktor Bayes tidak dapat diurai menjadi angka."

msgid "Bayes factor contours breaks must be positive."
msgstr "Patahan kontur faktor Bayes harus positif."

msgid "Bayes factor contours breaks must be increasing."
msgstr "Patahan kontur faktor Bayes harus ditingkatkan."

msgid "exp(Prior mean)"
msgstr "exp(Rerata priori)"

msgid "Prior mean"
msgstr "Rerata priori"

msgid "Prior standard deviation"
msgstr "Deviasi standar priori"

msgid "The default Bayes factor is based on unit information prior corresponding to a %1$s effect size, a normal distribution with mean = 0 and sd = %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Faktor Bayes bawaan berdasarkan priori informasi unit sesuai dengan %1$s "
"ukuran efek, distribusi normal dengan rerata = 0 dan sd = %2$s."

msgid "Bayesian Binomial Test"
msgstr "Uji Binomial Bayes"

msgid "- *Bayes factor*: If one-sided test is requested:\n  - BF+0: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the one-sided alternative hypothesis that the population mean is larger than the test value\n  - BF-0: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the one-sided alternative hypothesis that the population mean is smaller than the test value\n- BF0+: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the null hypothesis relative to the one-sided alternative hypothesis that the population mean is larger than the test value\n- BF0-: Bayes factor that quantifies evidence for the null hypothesis relative to the one-sided alternative hypothesis that that the population mean is smaller than the test value\n  - **p**: p-value corresponding to t-statistic."
msgstr ""
"- *Faktor Bayes*: Jika uji satu sisi diminta:\n"
"  - BF+0: Faktor Bayes yang menghitungkan bukti untuk hipotesis alternatif "
"satu sisi yang rerata populasi lebih besar dari nilai uji\n"
"  - BF-0: Faktor Bayes yang menghitungkan bukti untuk hipotesis alternatif "
"satu sisi yang rerata populasi lebih kecil dari nilai uji\n"
"- BF0+: Faktor Bayes yang menghitungkan bukti untuk hipotesis null relatif "
"ke hipotesis alternatif satu sisi yang rerata populasi lebih besar dari "
"nilai uji\n"
"- BF0-: Faktor Bayes yang menghitungkan bukti untuk hipotesis null relatif "
"ke hipotesis alternatif satu sisi yang rerata populasi lebih kecil dari "
"nilai uji\n"
"  - **p**: Nilai-p sesuai dengan statistik-t."

